<div class="col-md-12 popupwindow page-content">
	<div class=" formatting-help">
		<h3>Formatting Help</h3>
		<p>Use the table below for reference on how to format, descriptions, and criteria. Bold, italic, headings, URLs (web addresses), lists, and quotes.</p>
		<table class="table" >
			<tr>
				<th>What</th>
				<th>What You Write</th>
				<th>What You See</th>
